{"tid":1713882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"最終嘅出路？","createTime":"2019-11-12T21:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T21:41:34.000Z","uid":77865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3cecc3d45536cc6b61de9e82da0348243c906163","tid":1713882,"uid":77865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T21:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2054342341501416/posts/2495200150748964?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2054342341501416%2Fposts%2F2495200150748964%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOsls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=17a5a9e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2054342341501416/posts/2495200150748964?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n文中對現況嘅描述都啱<br />\n初期我都覺得一國兩制下五大訴求係唯一出路<br />\n但係政府嘅態度 警察嘅行動  法院排期次序<br />\n感覺上好似已經唔太可行 <br />\n香港人連主權都無 點樣五大訴求 真普選 <br />\n無論做咩好都唔可以違反一國嘅準則<br />\n香港獨立看似係最完美咁回應香港人嘅訴求<br />\n但係談何容易 中共實力雄厚 <br />\n另一方面等外國嘅救援 實際成效亦未知之數<br />\n究竟出路又係邊？"}]}